                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 5931/491.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President of the United States</gloss>
                        to the <gloss type="to">Shah of Persia</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">The White House</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1909-11-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 16, 1909</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I tender your majesty congratulations on the opening of the constitutional
                    parliament. The American people wish welfare and peace for Persia under the new
                    order of things.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wm. H. Taft.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
